{"tid":2285751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係我鍾意嘅女仔生日,但我寫咗封畀香港人嘅信","createTime":"2020-11-14T11:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T06:40:57.000Z","uid":322679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"441274bc1f124053731c94a3995cff0df24c757e","tid":2285751,"uid":322679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:12:59.000Z","msg":"今日係我鍾意嘅女仔生日<br />\n每年呢個時候我都會寫封信畀佢,寫低有咩我想同佢講<br />\n但今年,我越寫,越發覺呢封信其實適合每一個覺得自己係香港人嘅人<br />\n為香港嘅精神而努力嘅同路人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eE4sqtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeE4sqtE.jpg&h=5834fe5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5nmuVh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5nmuVh.jpg&h=5c87ada5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢唔會睇到,但都希望佢生日快樂<br />\n希望每個香港人都加油"},{"pid":"e7b148b799a53c1bd473da1b76d4e4074e0b19c2","tid":2285751,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed2dc133fd89e0f0354bbfd515b1b26c136340e0","tid":2285751,"uid":381265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T11:41:41.000Z","msg":"剩係見你手字已經濕濕地<br />\n睇埋內容直頭高潮反哂白眼"},{"pid":"ff436e84725e2d261f1a69d18969f4da0299413d","tid":2285751,"uid":151983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:30:12.000Z","msg":"睇到毛管戙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede7ed492b2fd340dca631eda6b7a2cbbab02b2d","tid":2285751,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"矯情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放棄啦"}]}